(mention of Gothi, Carmen apologeticum 810, problematic loss of faith during the persecution of Christians, cf. the discussion in Africa under Cyprianus after 250) and the 5th cent. (reference to the seizure of Rome by Alaric in 410?). In 480, C. is mentioned by Gennadius (Vir. ill. 15).
